      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MASSARO (2) was strongly supported last start when a short priced favourite and duly saluted winning by 5.5 lengths at Q Lakeside in a handy 25.03. Fair draw can see a good run and likes the trip. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card in scoring last start. In sparkling form and looks the one to beat again. POP SAID YES (5) has a strong record this track and trip with eight wins and three placings from 12 starts. Recorded a 1.75 lengths win (18.74) in a Free For All last time at Q Straight. Can feature with the right run. INTO OBLIVION (1) was out of the placings last time when seventh at this track (20.05) but scored four back at this track (19.87). Solid record here at the distance winning four races. Strong form has emerged from his last run. Bold showing expected. CASH ON DEMAND (8) can play a role in the finish without surprising.",
